# Controls what `gcloud builds submit` uploads as the build context. Without
# this file, gcloud falls back to .gitignore — which excludes all of
# instructions/, breaking the image build. Keep only what the image needs:
# codex/ (Dockerfile + entrypoint + task + config) and instructions/video-project
# + instructions/docs. Everything heavy/secret/irrelevant is excluded.
.git
**/node_modules
app
out
.codex
demo-repo
instructions/rendered
instructions/grants-tool-reference
**/.DS_Store
**/.env
**/*.key
**/.eleven_key
